

## python

```bash
virtualenv -ppython3.6 bosster
source ./bosster/bin/activate
pip install grpcio-tools

# after this command in python_client path will be generated
# service_pb2.py and service_pb2_grpc.py. DO NOT EDIT this files!
python -m grpc_tools.protoc -I. --python_out=./python_client --grpc_python_out=./python_client bosster.proto
```
